{"tid":2071650,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"代Frd Po：可立中學學生遭校方打壓 製造白色恐怖","createTime":"2020-06-20T04:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T05:46:10.000Z","uid":250634,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d8620ccc763281fdcc50fcd6ffa5bcdc4a4f630c","tid":2071650,"uid":250634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:15:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://lih.kg/1782994\" target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/1782994</a><br />\n之前呢間中學已經有教畜因為學生和你lunch除咗校呔同遮校徽，之後話認唔到係佢哋學生而唔開校門，之後仲要係canteen鬧咗20分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後最近，F3C班有同學係俗稱「Q版」嘅班相當中作出<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求缺一不可</span></span>嘅「五一」手勢<br />\n<br />\n上星期三6月10號3C班主任堂<br />\n可立中學<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">彭惠蘭校長</span></strong></span>進入3C班房<br />\n告知同學因為有<span style=\"color: red;\">「51」手勢</span>，所以唔可以印嗰張「Q版」班相，同埋比同學兩個選擇：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一 重拍一次Q版班照<br />\n第二 直接唔要張相</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰陣有學生問校長點解唔可以印張相<br />\n個校長説考慮而家個政治情況，同埋佢從事教育界好多年，加上上次有個文姓老師對學生提及違反老師中立原則言論事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢預測如果印咗張班相，預知到有人會因此炒作，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">怕影響學校聲譽同形象</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">F4都有相似情況</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n學生有自由有權力做自己想做嘅手勢同姿勢，但因為政治考慮，就可以咁冠冕堂皇咁抹殺了學生應有嘅自由，又話預知到定會有人用此炒作，所以就決定唔印學生嘅班相<br />\n呢一種政治打壓，究竟係<span style=\"color: gold;\">邊個將政治帶入學校</span>？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上之前校方同意學生喺校內派文宣，每層可以癡10張文宣，而家就出爾反爾，多次阻止學生於校內癡文宣同派文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望手足幫手煲大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾個校長知白色恐怖先會影響校譽同形象"},{"pid":"f2b1443ab7f5b0cdcfb20dc4283874152b345103","tid":2071650,"uid":250634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:16:09.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求幫推"},{"pid":"1d435dc2cae493f49b8f26ec8c8715b0010584d5","tid":2071650,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:17:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b978f8c025fd0e9dafc68cdaa5e201a89d470cc","tid":2071650,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"色色圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb9f4d8bddfb6d7911251b5ebff85b70b0fb6de","tid":2071650,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:17:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾高層"},{"pid":"ab38a8d6a38e6111be29d6a58e5564eb596aab32","tid":2071650,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:18:32.000Z","msg":"夠薑咪變42囉"},{"pid":"2372cf66539997b08f2ee4f3e7f5630ec0cc5359","tid":2071650,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"076876281455a8ed170f2bd5f94297f64628a41c","tid":2071650,"uid":166820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c0f9c90688db29ec18e6eef7db38ec7d4f3b17e","tid":2071650,"uid":230298,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"如果個校長係藍既 照痴文宣 搞大佢 ，到時教育局炒佢，無乜影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果會牽連既老師係黃，教育局落order 炒人，你地保唔保得住個老師？"},{"pid":"68d1037daf7004f790aaa6f33d1b8e6b08ac2040","tid":2071650,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾學校"},{"pid":"48de34e5a4ea19300649a3e4a7fd657b845aaa04","tid":2071650,"uid":1251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2b1443ab7f5b0cdcfb20dc4283874